Package antlr

Class IRTXTBaseVisitor<T>

java.lang.Object
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
antlr.IRTXTBaseVisitor<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRTXTVisitor<T>, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
IRImport
public class IRTXTBaseVisitor<T> extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T> implements IRTXTVisitor<T>
This class provides an empty implementation of IRTXTVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
